{"tid":1603094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印尼女記者遭克警射爆眼！右眼球破裂 視力減退","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:00:00.000Z","uid":222970,"like":55,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3db03b9122037bdfb25b7b556e0e2720f4eb7f3e","tid":1603094,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"印尼女記者遭克警射爆眼！右眼球破裂 視力減退<br />\n<br />\n今日（29日）網民發起「全球反極權大遊行」，防暴警察在港島多處驅趕示威者。警察於灣仔天橋撤退時表現驚慌，並曾開槍作掩護。其間有記者懷疑右眼中橡膠彈倒地，要由急救員治理，當時她神智清醒。據悉，醫生初步診斷後，指女記者的眼球破裂，視力「減退」，形容其情況與8.11尖沙咀警署外疑遭警布袋彈「爆眼」的少女類似。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該記者是一間本地印尼語媒體SUARA的全職員工，只配備一個簡單眼罩，而眼罩右眼位置裂開。救護車到場後，該名女記者可清楚講述自己受傷位置，並稱右眼感到痛楚。救護員將她抬上擔架，據悉送往東區醫院，暫無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190929/60097908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60097908&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=20fedef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60097908&h=f66f6265\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190929/60097908</a>"},{"pid":"fd49a6b737ccce674b18199487ca4c7d2691d1dc","tid":1603094,"uid":3135,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"死黑警 依單真係無得放過佢哋"},{"pid":"f1a85f4b3f12438703886940760eaee2de2afc75","tid":1603094,"uid":27432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n又水平射"},{"pid":"189944fac754032a1cd18ddcaee9bb78977dbf8e","tid":1603094,"uid":1436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:13:53.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同鄉"},{"pid":"edcddfebc743e872fd81da6b14100f436a771771","tid":1603094,"uid":9,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1a85f4b3f12438703886940760eaee2de2afc75","tid":1603094,"u